1
00:00:47,650 --> 00:00:51,003
Hey, Dave.

2
00:00:52,479 --> 00:00:52,960
Hello.

3
00:00:53,602 --> 00:00:55,094
Good morning, sunshine.

4
00:00:57,998 --> 00:00:58,881
You made breakfast?

5
00:00:59,122 --> 00:01:03,007
Yep. You were sleeping so peacefully, you know, I couldn't afford to wake you up.

6
00:01:05,543 --> 00:01:06,908
Those stupid tablets.

7
00:01:07,470 --> 00:01:11,435
I know, knocked you out, right? Anyway, how are you feeling now?

8
00:01:12,318 --> 00:01:16,668
I feel good. Even better knowing that I have you and you got my back.

9
00:01:17,117 --> 00:01:24,052
I always do. All right, so enjoy your meal. Uh, it may not taste as good as yours, but hey, I tried.

10
00:01:28,034 --> 00:01:28,452
Thank you.

11
00:01:28,596 --> 00:01:30,041
That's fine.

12
00:01:31,470 --> 00:01:36,239
No, really, thank you for everything.

13
00:01:36,448 --> 00:01:49,647
There we go again. Here we go again. Listen, I'm your husband. I signed up for this, remember? All right, so I got to run now, okay?

14
00:01:50,583 --> 00:01:51,521
You're not joining me?

15
00:01:52,250 --> 00:01:54,855
No, I'm not, but someone else is.

16
00:01:56,974 --> 00:01:57,007
Who?

